Conflicts: bluez,
Replaces: bluez,
Breaks: bluez (<< 5.66),
Description: BlueZ Bluetooth tools for AIC FCS960K
 BlueZ is the official Linux Bluetooth protocol stack. It is an
 open source project distributed under GNU General Public License (GPL).
 .
 This package contains the Bluetooth daemons and tools for the AIC FCS960K chip.
 It includes:
  - bluetoothd: Bluetooth daemon
  - bluetoothctl: Interactive Bluetooth control tool
  - hcitool, hciconfig: HCI configuration tools
  - btmgmt: Management interface tool
  - rfcomm, sdptool: Protocol tools
  - And other Bluetooth utilities

